    "{\"#\":429,\"createdAt\":\"2020-07-02T02:35:15.250363Z\",\"event\":{\"ReqFieldCustomTextSet\":{\"fid\":1,\"id\":{\"gr\":79},\"value\":[{\"//\":[{\"lit\":\"[04/12/2013: I also need to know which usecases are complete and which still need work. Usecases will often be a work in progress, filled with TODOs and TBDs, empty fields. I need a way to access the state of (in)completeness across my all usecases without having to click and manually read each one. ]\"}]},{\"bl\":{}},{\"lit\":\"When I'm revising UCs I want the following:\"},{\"ol\":[[{\"lit\":\"To know which UCs have bad tags, and how many: [DELETED] refs, invalid step refs, invalid UC refs.\"}],[{\"lit\":\"To know which UCs have these, and how many: TODOs, TBDs.\"}],[{\"lit\":\"To know which UCs have empty (mandatory) fields, and how many.\"}],[{\"lit\":\"To be able to see all of the above in context without having to open each UC.\"}],[{\"lit\":\"Total number of above.\"}],[{\"lit\":\"Ability to filter UC scope.\"}]]},{\"lit\":\"The pros usually add additional info to TODOs and TBDs such as who is responsible for the next step, when they expect to know, etc.\"},{\"bl\":{}},{\"lit\":\"It might be an idea to auto-populate new UCs with TODOs in each field and use that instead of considering empty fields a problem. Or maybe have the ability to switch empty fields on/off.\"}]}}}",
    "{\"#\":430,\"createdAt\":\"2020-07-02T02:35:48.811453Z\",\"event\":{\"GenericReqCreate\":{\"reqId\":80,\"reqTypeId\":10,\"values\":[]}}}",
