expectation?\"},{\"cb\":{\"code\":\"FB1 - 1,2,3  HMMM: 3?\\nFB2 - 1\\nFB3 - 1,4    HMMM: 1?\\nFB4 - 1,4    HMMM: 1? 4?\\nIV1 - 1,2,3  HMMM: 3?\\nIV2 - 1,2,3  HMMM: 3?\\nUC2 - 1,2,3  HMMM: 3?\\nMF1 - 1\\nMF2 - 2,3    HMMM: 3?\\nMF3 - 2,3    HMMM: 2?\\nMF4 - 4\"}},{\"ol\":[[{\"lit\":\"all MFs in the subject's backward & forward implication tree\"},{\"cb\":{\"code\":\"FB1 - 1,2\\nFB2 - 1\\nFB3 - 4\\nFB4 - ∅\\nIV1 - 1,2\\nIV2 - 1,2\\nUC2 - 1,2\\nMF1 - 1\\nMF2 - 2,3   ERROR: cycle\\nMF3 - 2,3   ERROR: cycle\\nMF4 - 4\"}}]]}]}}}",
