    "{\"#\":691,\"createdAt\":\"2020-07-16T09:11:54.808179Z\",\"event\":{\"ReqFieldCustomTextSet\":{\"fid\":1,\"id\":{\"gr\":110},\"value\":[{\"lit\":\"What would it be like as a \"},{\"mono\":\"++\"},{\"lit\":\" replacement for Github issues and/or use on an OSS project? How would I use this in conjunction with scalajs-react? Any github user can currently raise an issue in Github. I can also mention anyone on Github and they're get a notification. Any Github user can watch any issue in project. They can also watch all issues or just watch releases. \"},{\"issue\":{\"desc\":[{\"lit\":\"follow this thought properly later\"}],\"type\":1}}]}}}",
