    "{\"#\":787,\"createdAt\":\"2020-08-05T03:37:59.821319Z\",\"event\":{\"ReqFieldCustomTextSet\":{\"fid\":1,\"id\":{\"gr\":119},\"value\":[{\"lit\":\"Let's start with a real-world example:\"},{\"cb\":{\"attr\":[\"render\"],\"code\":\"node[style=filled fillcolor=\\\"#eeeeee\\\"]\\nFB1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ffc905\\\" label=\\\"FB1\\\\n(#NAᵈ)\\\"]\\nMF1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ffc905\\\" label=\\\"MF1\\\\n(#NAᵈ)\\\"]\\nIV1 [fillcolor=\\\"#f5f100\\\" label=\\\"IV1\\\\n(#A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV2 [fillcolor=\\\"#ffc905\\\" label=\\\"IV2\\\\n(#NAᵈ)\\\"]\\nIV3 [fillcolor=\\\"#f5f100\\\" label=\\\"IV3\\\\n(#A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR1\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR2 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR2\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR3 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR3\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR4 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR4\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\n\\nFB1 -> MF1 -> IV1 -> FR1,FR2\\nFR1 -> FR3\\nMF1 -> IV2\\nMF1 -> IV3 -> FR4\",\"lang\":\"dot\"}},{\"//\":[{\"lit\":\"(Note: Bold circle indicates a manual status; superscript ᵈ indicates a field default; later superscript ⁺ will indicate derivation.)\"}]},{\"bl\":{}},{\"lit\":\"Firstly, let's start replacing defaults with derivative tags where possible...\"},{\"bl\":{}},{\"lit\":\"And holy shit we run into a problem immediately. Should IV-{1,3} be changed to \"},{\"mono\":\"#R\"},{\"lit\":\", even those there's a manual assignment? Let's just try both ways.\"},{\"ol\":[[{\"lit\":\"Apply derivation\"},{\"cb\":{\"attr\":[\"render\"],\"code\":\"node[style=filled fillcolor=\\\"#eeeeee\\\"]\\nFB1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ffc905\\\" label=\\\"FB1\\\\n(#NA⁺)\\\"]\\nMF1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ffc905\\\" label=\\\"MF1\\\\n(#NA⁺)\\\"]\\nIV1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"IV1\\\\n(#R⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV2 [fillcolor=\\\"#ffc905\\\" label=\\\"IV2\\\\n(#NAᵈ)\\\"]\\nIV3 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"IV3\\\\n(#R⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR1\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR2 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR2\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR3 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR3\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR4 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR4\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\n\\nFB1 -> MF1 -> IV1 -> FR1,FR2\\nFR1 -> FR3\\nMF1 -> IV2\\nMF1 -> IV3 -> FR4\",\"lang\":\"dot\"}}],[{\"lit\":\"Reject IV2\"},{\"cb\":{\"attr\":[\"render\"],\"code\":\"node[style=filled fillcolor=\\\"#eeeeee\\\"]\\nFB1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FB1\\\\n(#R⁺)\\\"]\\nMF1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"MF1\\\\n(#R⁺)\\\"]\\nIV1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"IV1\\\\n(#R⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV2 [fillcolor=\\\"#bbbbbb\\\" label=\\\"IV2\\\\n(#REJ)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV3 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"IV3\\\\n(#R⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR1\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR2 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR2\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR3 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR3\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR4 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR4\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\n\\nFB1 -> MF1 -> IV1 -> FR1,FR2\\nFR1 -> FR3\\nMF1 -> IV2\\nMF1 -> IV3 -> FR4\",\"lang\":\"dot\"}}],[{\"lit\":\"Implement FR4\"},{\"cb\":{\"attr\":[\"render\"],\"code\":\"node[style=filled fillcolor=\\\"#eeeeee\\\"]\\nFB1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FB1\\\\n(#R⁺)\\\"]\\nMF1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"MF1\\\\n(#R⁺)\\\"]\\nIV1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"IV1\\\\n(#R⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV2 [fillcolor=\\\"#bbbbbb\\\" label=\\\"IV2\\\\n(#REJ)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV3 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"IV3\\\\n(#I⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR1\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR2 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR2\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR3 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR3\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR4 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR4\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\n\\nFB1 -> MF1 -> IV1 -> FR1,FR2\\nFR1 -> FR3\\nMF1 -> IV2\\nMF1 -> IV3 -> FR4\",\"lang\":\"dot\"}}],[{\"lit\":\"Implement FR1\"},{\"bl\":{}},{\"lit\":\"Two options here.\"},{\"bl\":{}},{\"lit\":\"(a) FR1 still appears as \"},{\"mono\":\"#ready_for_dev\"},{\"lit\":\" because FR3 hasn't been marked as implemented.\"},{\"cb\":{\"attr\":[\"render\"],\"code\":\"node[style=filled fillcolor=\\\"#eeeeee\\\"]\\nFB1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FB1\\\\n(#R⁺)\\\"]\\nMF1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"MF1\\\\n(#R⁺)\\\"]\\nIV1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"IV1\\\\n(#R⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV2 [fillcolor=\\\"#bbbbbb\\\" label=\\\"IV2\\\\n(#REJ)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV3 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"IV3\\\\n(#I⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR1\\\\n(#R⁺ ← #I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR2 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR2\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR3 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR3\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR4 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR4\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\n\\nFB1 -> MF1 -> IV1 -> FR1,FR2\\nFR1 -> FR3\\nMF1 -> IV2\\nMF1 -> IV3 -> FR4\",\"lang\":\"dot\"}},{\"lit\":\"(b) FR3 is automatically marked as \"},{\"mono\":\"#implemented\"},{\"lit\":\" too\"},{\"cb\":{\"attr\":[\"render\"],\"code\":\"node[style=filled fillcolor=\\\"#eeeeee\\\"]\\nFB1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FB1\\\\n(#R⁺)\\\"]\\nMF1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"MF1\\\\n(#R⁺)\\\"]\\nIV1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"IV1\\\\n(#R⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV2 [fillcolor=\\\"#bbbbbb\\\" label=\\\"IV2\\\\n(#REJ)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV3 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"IV3\\\\n(#I⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR1 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR1\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR2 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR2\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR3 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR3\\\\n(#I⁺)\\\"]\\nFR4 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR4\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\n\\nFB1 -> MF1 -> IV1 -> FR1,FR2\\nFR1 -> FR3\\nMF1 -> IV2\\nMF1 -> IV3 -> FR4\",\"lang\":\"dot\"}},{\"lit\":\"The purpose of this feature is to avoid users needing to manually go and re-tag everything. If we go with option (a) then users would have to manually go and re-tag all the children, meaning we've failed in the goal of this feature. Where as option (b) achieves this. And it makes sense. If users don't like the behaviour then they shouldn't create an umbrella issue and close it directly. But the ability to close an entire umbrella is very important and we can't exclude that from the solution. Option (b) it is.\"}],[{\"lit\":\"Implement FR2\"},{\"cb\":{\"attr\":[\"render\"],\"code\":\"node[style=filled fillcolor=\\\"#eeeeee\\\"]\\nFB1 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FB1\\\\n(#I⁺)\\\"]\\nMF1 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"MF1\\\\n(#I⁺)\\\"]\\nIV1 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"IV1\\\\n(#I⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV2 [fillcolor=\\\"#bbbbbb\\\" label=\\\"IV2\\\\n(#REJ)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV3 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"IV3\\\\n(#I⁺ ← #A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR1 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR1\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR2 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR2\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR3 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR3\\\\n(#I⁺)\\\"]\\nFR4 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR4\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\n\\nFB1 -> MF1 -> IV1 -> FR1,FR2\\nFR1 -> FR3\\nMF1 -> IV2\\nMF1 -> IV3 -> FR4\",\"lang\":\"dot\"}}]]},{\"lit\":\"And to compare to no derivation: ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑ ⇑\"},{\"cb\":{\"attr\":[\"render\"],\"code\":\"node[style=filled fillcolor=\\\"#eeeeee\\\"]\\nFB1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ffc905\\\" label=\\\"FB1\\\\n(#NAᵈ)\\\"]\\nMF1 [fillcolor=\\\"#ffc905\\\" label=\\\"MF1\\\\n(#NAᵈ)\\\"]\\nIV1 [fillcolor=\\\"#f5f100\\\" label=\\\"IV1\\\\n(#A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV2 [fillcolor=\\\"#bbbbbb\\\" label=\\\"IV2\\\\n(#REJ)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nIV3 [fillcolor=\\\"#f5f100\\\" label=\\\"IV3\\\\n(#A)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR1 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR1\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR2 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR2\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\nFR3 [fillcolor=\\\"#ccf000\\\" label=\\\"FR3\\\\n(#Rᵈ)\\\"]\\nFR4 [fillcolor=\\\"#00a80399\\\" label=\\\"FR4\\\\n(#I)\\\" penwidth=3]\\n\\nFB1 -> MF1 -> IV1 -> FR1,FR2\\nFR1 -> FR3\\nMF1 -> IV2\\nMF1 -> IV3 -> FR4\",\"lang\":\"dot\"}},{\"lit\":\"This looks like a good approach to me.\"}]}}}",
