    "{\"#\":851,\"createdAt\":\"2020-08-10T00:21:58.697726Z\",\"event\":{\"ReqFieldCustomTextSet\":{\"fid\":1,\"id\":{\"gr\":120},\"value\":[{\"h1\":[{\"lit\":\"Graph algorithm\"}]},{\"h4\":[{\"lit\":\"From \"},{\"req\":{\"gr\":119}}]},{\"ol\":[[{\"__\":[{\"lit\":\"Defaults are applied\"}]}],[{\"lit\":\"Start processing from roots and work down to leaves, for each node...\"}],[{\"lit\":\"Merge current node's manual or default values in to its children\"}],[{\"lit\":\"Start processing from leaves and working back to trees, for each node...\"}],[{\"lit\":\"Take the results of all its children, merge and (a) add to manual tag value if it differs, or (b) remove the default and add the merge results.\"}]]},{\"h4\":[{\"lit\":\"From \"},{\"req\":{\"gr\":117}}]},{\"ol\":[[{\"lit\":\"Start processing from roots and work down to leaves, for each node...\"}],[{\"lit\":\"Merge current node's manual or default values in to its children \"},{\"__\":[{\"lit\":\"unless the child has a manual value\"}]}],[{\"lit\":\"Start processing from leaves and working back to trees, for each node...\"}],[{\"lit\":\"Take the results of all its children, merge and (a) add to manual tag value if it differs, or (b) remove the default and add the merge results.\"}]]},{\"h4\":[{\"lit\":\"Done!\"}]},{\"lit\":\"Both blocks are identical except for the underlined parts:\"},{\"ul\":[[{\"lit\":\"the defaults step in \"},{\"req\":{\"gr\":119}},{\"lit\":\": applying it to \"},{\"req\":{\"gr\":117}},{\"lit\":\" doesn't change anything\"}],[{\"lit\":\"the extra condition in \"},{\"req\":{\"gr\":117}},{\"lit\":\": applying the bold bit to \"},{\"req\":{\"gr\":119}},{\"lit\":\" doesn't change the results\"}]]},{\"lit\":\"I think we're good!\"},{\"h1\":[{\"lit\":\"Combination algorithm\"}]},{\"lit\":\"The set of tags must be reduced inductively by taking two and returning one, until it is no longer possible. The rules for \"},{\"mono\":\"A |+| A\"},{\"lit\":\" are specified as part of config that the users maintains. If there is no rule for \"},{\"mono\":\"A₁ |+| A₂\"},{\"lit\":\" then both values \"},{\"mono\":\"{A₁ A₂}\"},{\"lit\":\" remain in the results.\"},{\"h1\":[{\"lit\":\"Provenance\"}]},{\"lit\":\"All inputs and calculations in the derivation must be maintained such that\"},{\"ul\":[[{\"lit\":\"they can be presented to a user as text (i.e. a multi-step formula)\"}],[{\"lit\":\"they can be used to create colour bars indicating all content considered\"}],[{\"lit\":\"empty values (i.e. relevant nodes with no tags) should also consume space in colour bars\"}]]}]}}}",
