    "{\"#\":894,\"createdAt\":\"2020-08-31T03:17:15.031095Z\",\"event\":{\"ReqFieldCustomTextSet\":{\"fid\":1,\"id\":{\"gr\":124},\"value\":[{\"lit\":\"Actually, I'm going to mark this as \"},{\"tag\":20},{\"lit\":\" for now. I'm not sure it would be a good idea for ReqTable for the following reasons:\"},{\"ul\":[[{\"lit\":\"RT is already very, very busy and there are already colours for tags. Colour bars on every row (even multiples per row!) might be too much\"}],[{\"lit\":\"There'd be no way of configuring it - it would be hardcoded on which would likely lead to annoyed users\"}],[{\"lit\":\"It gets complicated when you consider re-appearances. Would colour bars make sense if we've split a tag cell into multiple rows?\"}],[{\"lit\":\"this is a view-only change. It's trivial to just add it later if neededf\"}]]}]}}}",
    "{\"#\":895,\"createdAt\":\"2020-08-31T03:17:16.931393Z\",\"event\":{\"ReqFieldCustomTextSet\":{\"fid\":1,\"id\":{\"gr\":124},\"value\":[{\"lit\":\"Actually, I'm going to mark this as \"},{\"tag\":20},{\"lit\":\" for now. I'm not sure it would be a good idea for ReqTable for the following reasons:\"},{\"ul\":[[{\"lit\":\"RT is already very, very busy and there are already colours for tags. Colour bars on every row (even multiples per row!) might be too much\"}],[{\"lit\":\"There'd be no way of configuring it - it would be hardcoded on which would likely lead to annoyed users\"}],[{\"lit\":\"It gets complicated when you consider re-appearances. Would colour bars make sense if we've split a tag cell into multiple rows?\"}],[{\"lit\":\"this is a view-only change. It's trivial to just add it later if needed\"}]]}]}}}",
